@Deprecated
public class SweepSphere
extends java.lang.Object
implements Collidable

Sweep sphere implements a collidable moving sphere. Usually used to simulate simple physics for character entities in games. The sweep sphere can be used to check collision against a triangle or another sweep sphere.
